    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/917799d52158ae29798fc625da65680c.webp?t=1772198007\" width=426 height=49 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in first-person in a 3D dungeon crypt. Master one of several classes as you navigate procedurally-generated floors, where every card choice and tactical decision impacts your survival.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/1d58ad063fdbc2fe5acf5e45c90fa085.poster.avif?t=1772198007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/1d58ad063fdbc2fe5acf5e45c90fa085.webm?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/1d58ad063fdbc2fe5acf5e45c90fa085.mp4?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/044a5a72f6d86c6817a5c536b82e3a5d.webp?t=1772198007\" width=344 height=42 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your deck from hundreds of unique cards and dozens of status effects. Discover synergies between cards, chain complex combos, and adapt your strategy to face varied enemy encounters. No two runs will ever play the same!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d48f16bd540c9c5463876f9b94fd31e4.poster.avif?t=1772198007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d48f16bd540c9c5463876f9b94fd31e4.webm?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d48f16bd540c9c5463876f9b94fd31e4.mp4?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>   <br>   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/27f1387d2c73ea0940f096eb7e533072.webp?t=1772198007\" width=410 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every descent into the crypt is unique. Procedurally-generated maps with branching paths, multiple encounter types (minions, elites, bosses, treasures, events, shops, rest sites), and ever-changing enemy AI that keeps you at arm's length from certain death! Make pivotal choices in event encounters, experience witty and ominous creatures in your journey through the crypt, and find new ways of staying alive. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d0366ae7536a78588ee0004109d07d01.poster.avif?t=1772198007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d0366ae7536a78588ee0004109d07d01.webm?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/d0366ae7536a78588ee0004109d07d01.mp4?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/e4f73ce3fbff968adb624a42be9f6a3e.webp?t=1772198007\" width=126 height=33 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +300 unique cards and effects!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +100 enemies to encounter that have their own passive abilities, playing cards, and unique playstyle personalities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +200 items (potions, artifacts, secrets) to help you explore the Crypt!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over +75 engaging and choice-filled Events!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Three floors to conquer which are fully procedurally generated so no two runs feel the same!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in many different encounter types including: Combat, Shop, Treasure, Rest, Events, and more!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various difficulty levels and run modifiers to further enhance your Crypt experience!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/f010100d494d09ad2f3fcc814529cf10.poster.avif?t=1772198007\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/f010100d494d09ad2f3fcc814529cf10.webm?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1879270/extras/f010100d494d09ad2f3fcc814529cf10.mp4?t=1772198007\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
